---

## 1. What This Is

This repository defines CNIG — a conceptual framework for reasoning about system behavior under composition.

It is not a tool, system, or methodology.

It is a way of interpreting how systems behave when components interact.

---


## 2. Why CNIG Exists

In many systems:

- components behave correctly in isolation
- but system behavior changes unexpectedly when composed

CNIG exists to describe that gap.

It focuses on how structure influences outcomes **before execution occurs**.

